[Legend of Fuyao]

21
00:01:31,740 --> 00:01:34,510
~ Episode 3 ~

22
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:30,010
Clique Leader!

23
00:02:31,140 --> 00:02:32,760
Clique Leader!

24
00:02:35,290 --> 00:02:36,670
- What's the matter?
- It's bad.

25
00:02:36,670 --> 00:02:38,840
Zitie has escaped from his cage.

26
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:42,310
Search through the mountain immediately. Never let it escape the mountain.

27
00:03:52,550 --> 00:03:53,980
You've beaten him to death.

28
00:03:53,980 --> 00:03:56,240
I just pressed its Life Source Acupoint.

29
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:58,000
It will be unconscious for awhile.

30
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,910
Then what should we do now?

31
00:03:59,910 --> 00:04:01,400
Zitie is an ancient mythical beast.

32
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:03,140
It won't appear that easily.

33
00:04:03,140 --> 00:04:08,030
Its being here is most likely because it broke through its cage.

34
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:11,410
I guess in not over half an hour, people will come and get it.

35
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:16,790
Let's leave before they find out.

36
00:04:18,750 --> 00:04:22,030
Are you... not killing me anymore?

37
00:04:23,580 --> 00:04:25,080
You’re a smart person.

38
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:29,020
You should know that you have to be careful with your words.

39
00:04:29,020 --> 00:04:32,720
If you want to live, shut your mouth then.

40
00:04:35,130 --> 00:04:37,640
You're also a smart person.

41
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:41,110
You should also know that if you put on a mask for too long,

42
00:04:41,110 --> 00:04:44,280
you may forget who you really are.

43
00:04:56,220 --> 00:05:00,230
Hurry. Over there. Hurry.

44
00:05:00,230 --> 00:05:03,900
Hurry. Over there. Hurry!

45
00:05:18,340 --> 00:05:20,170
Who did this?

46
00:06:07,500 --> 00:06:09,500
Wait till I become Mystic Soul Clique Leader.

47
00:06:09,500 --> 00:06:12,010
I will surely help you get rid of your identity as a servant,

48
00:06:12,010 --> 00:06:15,340
then you can stand upright and I will let everyone know that

49
00:06:15,340 --> 00:06:17,690
you’re mine, Yan Jingchen’s lover.

50
00:06:35,460 --> 00:06:36,990
Fuyao.

51
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:46,530
I knew that you would be here.

52
00:06:51,380 --> 00:06:53,930
You almost made a big mistake yesterday.

53
00:06:57,140 --> 00:07:00,220
May I ask First Senior Brother, what did I do wrong?

54
00:07:01,300 --> 00:07:06,090
Yesterday, I was walking with Pei Yuan in the backyard and you appeared suddenly.

55
00:07:06,090 --> 00:07:09,000
You clearly knew that we got engaged.

56
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:21,040
Yes. What First Senior Brother lectured about is correct.

57
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,990
I don't know to love myself,

58
00:07:22,990 --> 00:07:24,790
can't accept that I'm of a lowly class,

59
00:07:24,790 --> 00:07:27,230
and always giving you troubles.

60
00:07:28,020 --> 00:07:30,160
Don't worry, First Senior Brother.

61
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:32,790
In the future, I won't bring you trouble anymore.

62
00:07:33,470 --> 00:07:35,880
Look at you. You still get impetuous as always.

63
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:37,800
I'm not done talking yet.

64
00:07:39,340 --> 00:07:41,250
First Senior brother, take care.

65
00:07:42,430 --> 00:07:44,200
Are you still angry?

66
00:07:44,930 --> 00:07:46,500
Fuyao,

67
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:52,040
my marring Pei Yuan doesn't mean my heart has changed.

68
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:54,770
Neither does it mean that I will not protect you from now on.

69
00:07:58,750 --> 00:08:01,040
First Senior Brother, what do you mean by that?

70
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:06,200
My marrying Pei Yuan is because we have no choice but to rely on her uncle’s power,

71
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:08,630
but my heart towards you didn’t change.

72
00:08:08,630 --> 00:08:12,590
In the future, if I get rooted in Capital Kun,

73
00:08:12,590 --> 00:08:16,230
I will marry you as my concubine and treat you as how it was before.

74
00:08:16,230 --> 00:08:17,680
You—

75
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:23,070
First Senior Brother, do you want me to be your second wife?

76
00:08:24,620 --> 00:08:27,980
I know you will suffer a bit,

77
00:08:27,980 --> 00:08:30,680
but this is the best method.

78
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:32,000
I've planned everything.

79
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:35,860
Wait till I'm going to Capital Kun. I will bring you along.

80
00:08:35,860 --> 00:08:38,970
Wait till the day you become my second wife,

81
00:08:38,970 --> 00:08:42,200
you can totally get rid of your identity as a servant then.

82
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:47,020
During that time, you'll be worry free of your livelihood and live a luxurious life.

83
00:08:48,760 --> 00:08:51,620
First Senior Brother, is this how you see me?

84
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:57,520
This is not what I wanted.

85
00:09:08,670 --> 00:09:13,850
Yuan'er, your father was worried about your marriage earlier.

86
00:09:13,850 --> 00:09:17,290
The way I see it now is that your loved one is here.

87
00:09:17,290 --> 00:09:20,890
Why don’t I represent your father today and propose your marriage to Clique Leader Yan?

88
00:09:20,890 --> 00:09:23,090
What do you think?

89
00:09:23,090 --> 00:09:25,110
Uncle.

90
00:09:25,110 --> 00:09:27,450
Prime Minister, how do I dare to?

91
00:09:27,450 --> 00:09:31,270
Chen'er, hurry and give the Prime Minister a toast.

92
00:09:35,820 --> 00:09:37,750
Thank you, Prime Minister, for favoring me.

93
00:09:37,750 --> 00:09:41,770
But my social class is significantly lower than Junior Sister's.

94
00:09:41,770 --> 00:09:45,830
Making such a connection to Junior Sister who is at a high class might wrong her.

95
00:09:45,830 --> 00:09:48,100
Yuan’er doesn’t care.

96
00:09:48,100 --> 00:09:50,200
What about you, my dear nephew?

97
00:09:57,490 --> 00:09:59,750
Thank you, Uncle Prime Minister.

98
00:10:17,110 --> 00:10:18,590
Junior Sister.

99
00:10:20,390 --> 00:10:22,310
Let me comb for you.

100
00:10:36,420 --> 00:10:39,270
Miss! Miss!

101
00:10:43,490 --> 00:10:45,690
- What happened?
- Mystic Black Section’s Fuyao,

102
00:10:45,690 --> 00:10:48,540
I saw that First Senior Brother was brought away by her again.

103
00:10:50,500 --> 00:10:52,200
Where are they?

104
00:10:52,930 --> 00:10:56,270
Fuyao, what else are you insisting about?

105
00:10:56,270 --> 00:10:59,190
I can give you freedom and a life you wanted,

106
00:10:59,190 --> 00:11:01,060
except that I can’t give you an official title.

107
00:11:01,060 --> 00:11:03,160
Even my heart is toward you.

108
00:11:04,670 --> 00:11:07,920
I don't need someone to give me the life I want.

109
00:11:09,150 --> 00:11:12,180
I can fight for it myself.

110
00:11:13,790 --> 00:11:16,320
Although I haven't read many books,

111
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:19,160
but I know

112
00:11:21,260 --> 00:11:23,320
when you like someone,

113
00:11:23,900 --> 00:11:26,160
you must be wholehearted.

114
00:11:28,580 --> 00:11:30,560
So it means that

115
00:11:31,630 --> 00:11:33,740
you don't want to be my concubine?

116
00:11:35,820 --> 00:11:38,260
Love cannot be shared.

117
00:11:38,890 --> 00:11:41,330
Why can you not understand?

118
00:11:43,370 --> 00:11:44,890
Pei Yuan comes from an aristocratic family.

119
00:11:44,890 --> 00:11:47,270
How can I offend her?

120
00:11:47,270 --> 00:11:50,350
You have many good qualities, but you are from a slave class after all.

121
00:11:50,350 --> 00:11:53,660
Father would never allow me to marry you.

122
00:11:53,670 --> 00:11:57,260
I have no choice but to marry Pei Yuan.

123
00:12:06,090 --> 00:12:09,980
Then, I'll-I'll give you my blessing.

124
00:12:16,570 --> 00:12:18,640
But I can't let you go.

125
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:21,990
Fuyao,

126
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:24,960
from the first time I saw you,

127
00:12:25,860 --> 00:12:30,080
from the first time I secretly taught you martial arts,

128
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:33,080
to every time you got into trouble,

129
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:37,290
I've always covered all for you and protected you.

130
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:52,260
Fuyao, marriage has never been the lasting affection of men and women.

131
00:12:52,260 --> 00:12:54,760
I am a man with ambitions.

132
00:12:54,760 --> 00:12:57,290
Between the future and lasting affection,

133
00:12:57,290 --> 00:12:59,260
I have no choice.

134
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:09,660
Afterwards,

135
00:13:12,910 --> 00:13:15,340
I won't bother First Senior Brother anymore.

136
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:21,150
Fuyao!

137
00:13:45,460 --> 00:13:47,800
Why doesn't Miss go to tear that bitch apart?

138
00:13:47,800 --> 00:13:50,420
They actually dared to meet behind Miss' back?!

139
00:13:50,420 --> 00:13:54,050
Miss, if you can't bear to lose First Senior Brother, I'll tie up that little bitch today.

140
00:13:54,050 --> 00:13:55,490
Let her die in the wilderness.

141
00:13:55,490 --> 00:13:58,270
Then, no one can destroy your marriage.

142
00:13:58,270 --> 00:13:59,980
Miss.

143
00:14:05,250 --> 00:14:07,110
Miss, I am A'Lie!

144
00:14:07,110 --> 00:14:10,540
You lowly slaves just have lowly lives as ants.

145
00:14:10,540 --> 00:14:12,220
You actually dared to steal the item that I want?

146
00:14:12,220 --> 00:14:15,130
Miss! Miss!

147
00:14:15,130 --> 00:14:16,930
Miss!

148
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:23,640
The things that I want never fall through.

149
00:14:23,640 --> 00:14:25,170
Even if they are ruined,

150
00:14:25,170 --> 00:14:27,350
they can only be mine.

151
00:14:27,350 --> 00:14:29,430
I cannot forgive you.

152
00:14:29,430 --> 00:14:32,370
I'll make you wish you were dead.

153
00:15:25,700 --> 00:15:27,610
Senior Brother, have you entered for the game?

154
00:15:27,610 --> 00:15:29,570
Me? My skills aren't good enough.

155
00:15:29,570 --> 00:15:31,100
The Hunting and Fighting Game is so dangerous.

156
00:15:31,100 --> 00:15:32,900
I think I should forget it.

157
00:15:32,900 --> 00:15:35,160
- I don't know who has entered.
- Right.

158
00:15:35,160 --> 00:15:37,500
Let's take a look at the front. Let's go.

159
00:15:54,530 --> 00:15:56,990
What? Isn't this the lowly slave from Mystic Black Section?

160
00:15:56,990 --> 00:15:59,130
That's right. Even she dares to enter into the Hunting and Fighting Game.

161
00:15:59,130 --> 00:16:00,800
Does she not know her place?

162
00:16:00,800 --> 00:16:03,290
A lowly slave actually is able to compete with us.

163
00:16:03,290 --> 00:16:06,930
If word gets out, won't it be the biggest joke of our Mystic Soul Clique?

164
00:16:35,510 --> 00:16:38,200
First Elder Brother, you—

165
00:16:39,350 --> 00:16:40,610
Why?

166
00:16:40,610 --> 00:16:41,870
What "why?"

167
00:16:41,870 --> 00:16:43,360
Why did you send in the application?

168
00:16:43,360 --> 00:16:45,580
Why do you enter in the Hunting and Fighting Game?

169
00:16:45,590 --> 00:16:47,460
The Hunting and Fighting Game?

170
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:50,680
- I don't know.
- You're even lying.

171
00:16:50,680 --> 00:16:54,290
If you didn't personally apply, why then will your name be in the Jade Stone Wall?

172
00:16:56,210 --> 00:16:59,990
So, First Elder Brother does not differentiate between right and wrong,

173
00:16:59,990 --> 00:17:01,120
and comes here to slander me?

174
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:02,870
Slander?

175
00:17:02,870 --> 00:17:06,710
Only with the participant's blood as their signature on the application,

176
00:17:06,710 --> 00:17:09,800
can their name appear on the roster.

177
00:17:10,400 --> 00:17:12,830
Look at you. The pinprick is still there.

178
00:17:12,830 --> 00:17:15,470
Could it be someone else signed up for you?

179
00:17:18,420 --> 00:17:20,330
When was this poked?

180
00:17:20,330 --> 00:17:22,320
Why can't I remember?

181
00:17:25,180 --> 00:17:29,800
Fuyao, are you still bitter over what happened yesterday?

182
00:17:31,930 --> 00:17:34,000
How can you be so stubborn?

183
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:36,960
Just with your measly martial arts, how many levels do you think you can pass?

184
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:39,310
You clearly know that if you enter, I'd have to protect you.

185
00:17:39,310 --> 00:17:40,800
If I protect you, I'll get distracted.

186
00:17:40,800 --> 00:17:43,630
Then, do you want me to focus on the competition or you?

187
00:17:43,630 --> 00:17:45,840
What do you want me to do?

188
00:17:48,500 --> 00:17:52,500
Originally, I thought it was out of your concern

189
00:17:52,500 --> 00:17:54,980
that you spoke to me.

190
00:17:54,980 --> 00:17:57,810
Unexpectedly, in Senior Brother's heart,

191
00:17:57,810 --> 00:17:59,680
I'm just a burden to you.

192
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:01,140
You—

193
00:18:01,140 --> 00:18:03,660
Although I didn't sign up,

194
00:18:03,660 --> 00:18:06,090
even if I were to enter the Hunting and Fighting Game,

195
00:18:06,090 --> 00:18:08,530
I would never drag you down.

196
00:18:08,530 --> 00:18:10,080
Fuyao,

197
00:18:10,490 --> 00:18:11,890
despite my earnest and well-meaning advice,

198
00:18:11,890 --> 00:18:14,040
are you still going to willfully persist in your stubborn ways?

199
00:18:14,930 --> 00:18:17,030
You let me down too much.

200
00:18:19,600 --> 00:18:21,640
You're the one to disappoint people.

201
00:18:32,330 --> 00:18:37,040
[Roster of Competitors]

202
00:18:37,040 --> 00:18:40,620
[Fuyao]

203
00:18:40,620 --> 00:18:42,170
Teacher.

204
00:18:43,860 --> 00:18:45,580
Come in.

205
00:18:51,330 --> 00:18:53,140
What is it?

206
00:18:53,140 --> 00:18:56,600
Has Teacher remembered Fuyao from Mystic Black Section?

207
00:18:56,600 --> 00:18:57,610
She has filled out the application

208
00:18:57,610 --> 00:18:59,840
and wants to enter the Hunting and Fighting Game.

209
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:03,310
Yes. The rules of the Hunting and Fighting Game are more than one hundred.

210
00:19:03,310 --> 00:19:07,030
How can it be messed up to a slave servant to mess up?

211
00:19:07,030 --> 00:19:11,300
This Fuyao doesn't fear anything because First Senior Brother treats her so well.

212
00:19:13,270 --> 00:19:16,050
She is a slave servant who cleans for Jingchen.

213
00:19:16,050 --> 00:19:19,640
They've grown up together, so it's natural he favors her.

214
00:19:19,640 --> 00:19:22,340
This is only out of Jingchen's warm heart.

215
00:19:22,340 --> 00:19:24,660
If she bothers you,

216
00:19:24,660 --> 00:19:26,530
why don't you kill her?

217
00:19:26,530 --> 00:19:30,530
If I kill her, Senior Brother will think I cannot tolerate people.

218
00:19:30,530 --> 00:19:34,830
But how can I sleep peacefully if I leave her alone?

219
00:19:34,830 --> 00:19:38,970
You have taken some countermeasures, haven't you?

220
00:19:38,970 --> 00:19:42,380
I want to ask Teacher to allow her to enter the competition.

221
00:19:42,380 --> 00:19:46,940
With her measly martial arts skills, she'll die in the first round.

222
00:19:47,470 --> 00:19:48,900
All right.

223
00:19:48,900 --> 00:19:50,430
Father!

224
00:19:58,250 --> 00:20:01,260
Teacher and Senior Brother have something to talk about,

225
00:20:01,260 --> 00:20:02,530
so I will excuse myself.

226
00:20:02,530 --> 00:20:04,100
Go then.

227
00:20:08,780 --> 00:20:11,690
What do you have to say?

228
00:20:11,690 --> 00:20:14,670
It's fishy in the applications for the Hunting and Fighting Game this time.

229
00:20:14,670 --> 00:20:16,930
Fuyao definitely couldn't have voluntarily signed up.

230
00:20:16,930 --> 00:20:19,960
Your son believes there has been a misunderstanding.

231
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:22,130
It's Fuyao again?

232
00:20:23,570 --> 00:20:24,970
You're even lying.

233
00:20:24,970 --> 00:20:29,120
Only with the participant's blood as their signature on the application,

234
00:20:29,120 --> 00:20:32,100
can their name appear on the roster.

235
00:20:32,100 --> 00:20:34,450
Look at you. The pinprick is still there.

236
00:20:34,450 --> 00:20:37,030
Could it be someone else signed up for you?

237
00:20:37,640 --> 00:20:39,390
It clearly wasn't me.

238
00:20:39,390 --> 00:20:41,330
Who was it exactly?

239
00:20:42,670 --> 00:20:45,990
Father, Fuyao is slow-witted with poor martial arts.

240
00:20:45,990 --> 00:20:50,030
Letting her join the game will not bring any benefit to our sect and will only bring us shame.

241
00:20:50,030 --> 00:20:51,590
Besides, according to the rules,

242
00:20:51,590 --> 00:20:53,160
Fuyao originally wasn't a student of Mystic Main Section.

243
00:20:53,160 --> 00:20:54,860
She isn't supposed to be in the office.

244
00:20:54,860 --> 00:20:58,790
If you disqualify her, it is very reasonable.

245
00:20:58,790 --> 00:21:01,610
Disqualify her?

246
00:21:03,170 --> 00:21:05,560
You make it sound easy.

247
00:21:05,560 --> 00:21:08,240
The Hunting and Fighting Game has been going on for more than one hundred and twenty years.

248
00:21:08,240 --> 00:21:13,030
Unless someone died, no one has ever backed out of the competition.

249
00:21:13,030 --> 00:21:15,080
This is a rule.

250
00:21:15,080 --> 00:21:17,480
Since she broke Mt. Mystic Soul's rules,

251
00:21:17,480 --> 00:21:19,970
she must bear the consequences.

252
00:21:19,970 --> 00:21:23,910
But-But she's nothing more than a lowly girl.

253
00:21:23,910 --> 00:21:26,070
She was born a servant,

254
00:21:26,070 --> 00:21:29,380
so signing up for the game is a crime punishable by death.

255
00:21:29,380 --> 00:21:31,410
Now, I'm just fulfilling her wish.

256
00:21:31,410 --> 00:21:33,060
- What else do you want me to do?
- Father—

257
00:21:33,060 --> 00:21:34,700
Stop talking.

258
00:21:39,910 --> 00:21:45,260
